- `src/lib/healthScore.ts` — instant-feedback mirror for the page
- `server/tools/runner.js` — register `score_financial_health`
- `server/tools/definitions.js` — JSON schema for the agent
- `server/agent/systemPrompt.js` — capability advertised
- `server/index.js` — `POST /api/health/score` endpoint
- `tests/server/health.test.js` (new) — 5 cases

